        "preparation": "* Review project requirements and rubric\n* Print copies of the Data for Social Good Project Planning Guide (one for each student)\n* Check the [**Teacher's Lounge**](https://forum.code.org/t/csa-3-10-data-for-social-good-project/37894) for verified teachers on the CSA Forum to find additional strategies or resources shared by fellow teachers",
