      "position": 4,
      "properties": {
        "description": "You will finish developing your store management program. Be sure to consider the feedback you received from your code review as you work on your program. First, let's revisit the Data for Social Good Project Planning Guide to make sure you have included everything you need to meet the project requirements.",
